description: It's Aphrodite's IX first mission to kill a very prominent politician. Moments before of starting her mission meets a man she thinks he has seen before. Why she can't remember anything and who's is this man?

volume.name: Top Cow Classics in Black and White: Aphrodite IX

description: The Magdalena is back! Straight from the pages of The Darkness, the Magdalena returns to star in her own three issue story arc. Brought to you by Joe Benitez (Darkness), Marcia Chen (Ascension) and Joe Weems (Fathom), this first issue takes place before the "Spear of Destiny" story line in The Darkness. The Magdalena, holy servant of the Catholic Church, is sent to a rural orphanage in France to investigate a series of killings reputed to be have been performed by a vampire. Meanwhile, Father Jasper, a priest from the Netherlands, arrives at the Vatican to speak with Cardinal Innocent, bringing with him ancient relics he found hidden in his church, which could spell the downfall of all Christianity. Don't miss out on what is sure to be one of the hottest books of 2000!

volume.name: Top Cow Classics in Black and White: Magdalena

description:
A giant ball of light was heading to Earth, when it flashed everyone in utero was changed.

Years later there was an earth quake a a local elementary school. When pieces of the school started to fall a young boy gave an example of his incredible strength. What will happen to these children with incredible power? How will the world react to them?

description: Banded together to protect the earth, G-Force is a team of five highly trained teenagers who keep the world safe from all manner of evil threats! Using an array of advanced weapons and even-more-advanced vehicles, the team best known for their 1970's cartoon series is set to be taken into the 21st Century by some of the top talents in comics! The Wait is OVER! Sandy Frank Productions, Top Cow Productions and Alex Ross proudly Present G-Force, The Battle of the Planets. Yes it's true. This July, the hottest book of 2002 takes off, written by Munier Sharief (Battle Chasers) and newcomer penciler extraordinaire Wilson Tortosa, with story layouts, art direction and COVERS by ALEX ROSS! Join Mark, Jason, Tiny, Keyop, and Princess on all their adventures to save the earth from the evil Zoltar and the forces of Spectra!
name: Trial By Fire

volume.name: Top Cow Classics in Black and White: Battle of the Planets

description: Chernobyl nuclear power plant, april 26, 1986. Some dark creature arise from the fall-out and request the pages that have been stolen. Then another alien winged girl is found in the gardens of a research center. She is half dead and holds and strange scroll of pages. The woman that finds her is Andromeda. The man that protects the woman is Lucien. In the moments that follow, a whole new story is set in motion, new unwilling interveners now participate in a thousand year old war between two species from another world...

volume.name: Top Cow Classics in Black and White: Ascension

description: A gripping tale of supernatural menace and gripping horror reveals monsters living among us! As a member of the paramilitary paranormal police force known as the Nightwatch, Mason Black devoted his life to fighting the hidden monster underworld. But the Nightwatch had corruption at its very core, so Mace did what no one had ever done before: he quit. Now on his own, he faces a deadly threat in New Orleans: an evil that threatens to destroy both the Nightwatch and the human-monster truce they defend. Can Mace unravel the truth in time? For more information, see the feature article.
name: Book One

description: A gripping tale of supernatural menace and gripping horror continues! Former Nightwatch operative Mason Black learns more about the fearsome creature known as Proteus. All of New Orleans' monster underworld has reason to dread Proteus, but that's not why Mace is going up against him. Black's motive is as personal as they come: He's fighting to redeem his very soul!
name: Book Two

description: A gripping tale of supernatural menace and gripping horror concludes! The explosive ending finds Mace Black investigating an abandoned Louisiana orphanage. But these walls haven't contained human children for years. And if there is anything inside, it isn't looking for its Mommy. Don't miss the action as Mace and Proteus face off in a battle to the death!
name: Book Three
